titleText: Designing a visual identity for a guitarstore
descriptionText: For my first semester exam at DMJX, I created a visual identity, an interactive asset generator, and an animated logo for a fictional guitar store called Rabalder.
description2Text: Here I have animated the logo using Processing.
description3Text: This is an asset generator created in Processing. It produces posters using sound input. Users can adjust both text and colors, making it easy to customize to fit different events.
